data.description: Your search ends here! 3 Bed, 2 Bath Ranch-style home situated in growing Cottage Grove neighborhood, just right for a young family or investment property. A roomy front porch opens to a uniquely beautiful spacious living room with tons of natural light. Seamlessly continues to a large kitchen ready to host social gatherings or family meals without feeling cramped or separated from the fun at the stove. Convenient laundry room directly off kitchen makes cleanup a cinch. The primary bedroom is split from smaller bedrooms and bath, offers plenty of room, a huge walk-in closet, and full bath.The back deck and yard are huge,  You have to see this beautiful home.
